---
// About Section with personal information and professional background
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Effects -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent/5 via-background to-primary/5"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-muted/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground border border-border mb-4">
        About Me
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Crafting Digital <span class="holographic">Experiences</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        I'm a passionate full-stack developer with a love for creating meaningful digital solutions that make a difference.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Profile Image -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-purple-500/20 p-1">
          <div class="aspect-square bg-gray-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <img 
              src="/portfolio_headshot.png" 
              alt="Sanjay Dhandapani - Full Stack Developer"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating Cards -->
        <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 bg-blue-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-500">3+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Years Exp</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-purple-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-500">50+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Projects</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            I'm a dedicated Full Stack Developer based in <strong>Tamil Nadu, India</strong>, with a passion for 
            building innovative web applications and scalable software solutions. My journey in technology 
            started with curiosity and has evolved into a comprehensive skill set spanning both frontend 
            and backend development.
          </p>
         
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Currently pursuing my <strong>Bachelor's in Computer Science and Engineering</strong>, I combine 
            academic knowledge with hands-on experience to deliver high-quality solutions. I specialize in 
            modern technologies like <strong>React, Node.js, TypeScript</strong>, and cloud platforms.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            When I'm not coding, you'll find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open-source 
            projects, or sharing knowledge with the developer community. I believe in continuous learning 
            and staying updated with industry trends.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Quick Facts -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">üéì Education</div>
            <div class="font-semibold">B.E Computer Science</div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">üìç Location</div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Tamil Nadu, India</div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">üíº Status</div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Available for Work</div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">üéØ Focus</div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Full Stack Development</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Action Buttons -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-6">
          <a 
            href="/resume.pdf" 
            target="_blank"
            class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3M3 17V7a2 2 0 012-2h6l2 2h6a2 2 0 012 2v10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
            Download Resume
          </a>
          
          <a 
            href="#contact" 
            class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          >
            Let's Connect
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .holographic {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4, #10b981);
    background-size: 400% 400%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    animation: holographic 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes holographic {
    0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    @apply shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(59, 130, 246), rgb(147, 51, 234));
    color: white;
  }
  
  .btn-secondary {
    @apply bg-transparent border-2 hover:text-white;
    border-color: rgb(59, 130, 246);
    color: rgb(59, 130, 246);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: rgb(59, 130, 246);
  }
</style>
